2. Navigates to Recipe section.
3. Applies diet filters.
4. Views personalized recipes.
5. Provides rating/feedback.

For Contributors:

1. Contributor logs in.
2. Clicks â€œSubmit New Recipe.â€
3. Fills structured form.
4. Recipe auto-publishes (if privileged) OR goes to Admin review.
5. Admin approves/rejects.

