# ğŸ“ User Stories & Acceptance Criteria

---

## 1ï¸âƒ£ Submit New Recipe Button

### User Story
As a Patient, I want to click on â€œSubmit New Recipeâ€ so that I can submit recipes for review.

### Acceptance Criteria

Given the patient is logged in  
When the patient clicks â€œSubmit New Recipeâ€  
Then the New Recipe Form is displayed  

---

## 2ï¸âƒ£ Identify User Type

### User Story
As an Admin, I want the system to identify the type of user submitting a recipe so that approval rules are applied correctly.

### Acceptance Criteria

Given user selects role  
When recipe is submitted  
Then role is stored  

Given role = Doctor (privileged)  
When submitted  
Then recipe auto-publishes  

Given role = Patient/Caregiver  
When submitted  
Then recipe goes to Admin review  

---

## 3ï¸âƒ£ Mandatory Fields Validation

### User Story
As a Contributor, I want mandatory fields enforced so that complete recipes are submitted.

### Acceptance Criteria

Given mandatory fields are empty  
When user clicks submit  
Then submit button remains disabled  

Given all mandatory fields are filled  
When submitted  
Then recipe is saved successfully  

---

## 4ï¸âƒ£ Filter Recipes by Diet

### User Story
As a Patient, I want to filter recipes by diet type so that I can easily find suitable meals.

### Acceptance Criteria

Given patient selects Low-Fiber  
When filter is applied  
Then only Low-Fiber recipes are displayed  

---

## 5ï¸âƒ£ Rating & Feedback

### User Story
As a Patient, I want to rate and review recipes so that others can benefit.

### Acceptance Criteria

Given rating selected (1â€“5)  
When submitted  
Then rating is stored and displayed  

Given feedback exceeds 200 characters  
When submitted  
Then validation error appears  

---

## 6ï¸âƒ£ Save Preferences

### User Story
As a Patient, I want to save diet preferences so that I donâ€™t reselect filters every time.

### Acceptance Criteria

Given user selects filters  
When â€œSave Preferencesâ€ is clicked  
Then preferences are saved in profile  

---

## 7ï¸âƒ£ Admin Approval Workflow

### User Story
As an Admin, I want to approve or reject submitted recipes so that only verified content is published.

### Acceptance Criteria

Given recipe is pending  
When Admin approves  
Then recipe becomes visible  

Given Admin rejects  
When reason entered  
Then contributor receives notification  

